1. DEFINITIONS
-------------
"Software" refers to the Porfin platform, including but not limited to:
- Frontend Next.js application and user interfaces
- Backend FastAPI services and microservices
- AI/ML models, training data, and inference systems
- WhatsApp integration components
- Documentation and supporting materials
- Database schemas and data structures
