- Business logic and workflows

"Service" refers to the Software provided as a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform.

"Customer" refers to healthcare professionals and organizations in Brazil authorized to access the Service.

2. LICENSE GRANT
---------------
Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, Porfin grants Customer a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable right to:
a) Access and use the Service through authorized interfaces
b) Process data within the defined LGPD compliance framework
c) Integrate with approved third-party services via official APIs
d) Store customer data in compliance with healthcare regulations
e) Process WhatsApp messages per Business API terms

3. RESTRICTIONS
--------------
Customer shall not, and shall not permit others to:
a) Redistribute any component or create derivative works
b) Modify source code, models, or configurations
c) Reverse engineer the platform or AI systems
d) Sublicense or transfer access rights
