g) Audit trail maintenance requirements

6. DATA PROTECTION
-----------------
Porfin shall process personal data in accordance with:
a) Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados (LGPD)
b) Healthcare-specific data protection requirements
c) Industry standard security practices
d) Customer's documented instructions

